text: Kang Kum-song (, born 1 May 1998) is a North Korean freestyle wrestler. He won silver in the men's 57kg division at the 18th Asian Games in Jakarta- Palembang, Indonesia, 2018. ==References== ==External links== * FILA profile Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:North Korean male sport wrestlers Category:Wrestlers at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games
